{"type": "article", "id": 2299, "title": "混凝土旋扭把手", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-10T23:53:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222341SmGczAWxF137eN8n.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t第一眼看到这一系列的旋扭把手，你会不会以为是哪家店又推出了新的蛋糕？最近，年轻设计师 Grey Hensey 设计了一系列灰色混凝土材质的把手。早在 Grey Hensey 大学时期，他就已经开始尝试研究混泥土的使用与设计。这个系列的把手在小巧玲珑的造型下结合混凝土的粗糙外表，给人视觉与触觉上的强劲冲击力。定价 15.97 美元，<a href=\"http://www.kastconcrete.com/shop/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052223388ayI4PCHsVqj5twT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222339CyiBPl6LcugHWrxw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052223392mLWS95NOxEXbt61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052223402f48ZJlGuhKe3UwC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}